item.description:
Hi All,

Well our season has ended and I think we should celebrate the fantastic summer we had for beach volleyball! We had a phenominal season with a great group of players!!

Come to Paddy's in Portsmouth for some food, drinks and pool! The website is: paddysgrille.com. Check out the menu and the pricing. Feel free to bring a guest or two. I am asking everyone to email me famous or infamous moments, phrases and situations you remember from the season. I am going to gather all of the information and put together a fun trivia game with prizes. Awards will also be handed out!

I hope to see you all there!!! Only 7 months until we will be back on the beach again!!

Lori
